title: Ultimate Ubuntu 2.0 GAMERS x86 (official)
description:
this is the (x86 only) "ultimate-edition-2.0-gamers.iso" i downloaded from http://ultimateedition.info/ exactly as i got it, untouched, untampered.

Burn the iso to a dvd and then boot from it.

I tried it out on a spare pc coz it looks pretty funky (you can see where Windows 7 nicked many of it's new gui ideas from). Unfortunatly i couldn't install decent drivers for my old 5900XT so it wouldn't go higher than 800x600 in crap mode... (sigh) - so watch out if you have an old nVidea card.

I'll seed most days from about 2pm to 11pm GMT


:-)
